{"tid":2189489,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"6000多人因「雲養貓」被騙上億元","createTime":"2020-09-05T02:39:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-05T03:09:42.000Z","uid":225931,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2c40d74097fb44208cd0f3dd53b81ad523cc3d98","tid":2189489,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T02:39:52.000Z","msg":"在「吸貓經濟」推動下，雲養貓APP竟暗藏各種詐騙套路。<br />\n<br />\n近日，多家媒體報道一款名叫「喵喵」的雲養貓軟件打著「躺賺」的旗號進行詐騙。<br />\n<br />\n該APP中包含高回報、低風險等誘惑性詞語。一些受害者表示，最開始在貼吧看到一條廣告，稱在網上養貓就能賺錢，且有高額回報。這正是該APP的推廣套路：通過網上发布吸引用戶添加微信下載APP。<br />\n<br />\n8月12日，該APP突然無法登錄，隨後相關工作人員相繼「消失」。受害者說，他們購買虛擬貓咪後不僅沒有獲得回報，本金也被卷走。<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，目前涉及金額已達幾億元，有6000多人報案，每個人的受騙金額在兩三千元到十多萬元之間。<br />\n<br />\n實際上，這種詐騙方式是披著養貓外衣的「互助盤」，即通過用高收益無風險來誘惑投資者投錢，通過老投資者的資金給新投資者支付利息，但最終資金流入平台建立方。"},{"pid":"507f6ae8a84373feb029ae8556b2dfa2c37defc1","tid":2189489,"uid":52839,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T02:40:45.000Z","msg":"養貓都賺到錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"523184e29e5aebe7c25d570b057e9b9067eb379e","tid":2189489,"uid":155095,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T02:41:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oqgMn7emgQE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DoqgMn7emgQE&d=RlZLtXxvTyjhSejQ4AJs47yOm5tzSGwlZJ%2FCF8Wpw90%3D&h=e0fba68a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oqgMn7emgQE</a>"},{"pid":"13394881b13c630a47f4a3cdfdb9b32b2fedd1ef","tid":2189489,"uid":61210,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T02:41:25.000Z","msg":"Crypto Kitty?"},{"pid":"d6fa585c4887cd86a6c8f0c8c94bd1acdc8856ae","tid":2189489,"uid":18241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T02:44:11.000Z","msg":"電子貓"},{"pid":"6221c3430d8b7bd1d299ff8113428c12865151d9","tid":2189489,"uid":82175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T02:51:43.000Z","msg"